            <p>Mainly two type of review system are use open loop and close loop system. Medzoid use close loop reviews system it means only those patients can give doctor feedback those complete their consultation with these doctor it is the major difference with open loop in which anyone can give any doctor may be possible these group never consult these doctors.</p>
            <p>We are encourage patients to give their reviews with each appointments so Medzoid reviews are not showing only highly happy or unhappy patients.</p>
